plot: Mackey must recover the stolen evidence from a drug bust before Aceveda is able to pin the theft on him.

Strike-Team launches an illegal wiretap against the Armenian mafia organization. Julien sees something illegal go down in the police raid. Claudette and Dutch get to know the mighty dangerous Armenian head of the operation while Vic finds out a diagnosis of one of his children that puts pressure into the investigation of a missing police vehicle started by Captain Aceveda.—AnduG8
